strategy.description: Map HGH feedGuid values to actual RSS feed URLs

steps.description: Verify these URLs are valid RSS feeds and contain the referenced tracks
These custom GUIDs may map to specific feed URLs or be generated from feed URLs
Investigate the main domains hosting these feeds
For tracks not found in discovered feeds, manually search for artist/album feeds

recommendations: Start with the discovered feed URLs to see if they contain the HGH tracks
Check if feedGuid values are UUIDs generated from feed URLs
Focus on domains that appear multiple times in the playlist
Consider reaching out to ChadF about the feedGuid mapping system
